<subSubSection pageId="178" pageNumber="457" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="178.[1445,2651,724,993]" pageId="178" pageNumber="457">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1447,1804,885,914]" pageId="178" pageNumber="457">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The IUCN Red List as a separate species from the Dusky Rice Rat (
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Tomes" baseAuthorityYear="1860" box="[1812,2006,924,953]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Melanomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="178" pageNumber="456" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="caliginosus">M. caliginosus</taxonomicName>
